i\" || ''[[Billa (2007 film)|Billa]]'' || Yuvan Shankar Raja\n|-\n|\"Iravil Bayandhen\" || rowspan=\"3\" | ''[[Taare Zameen Par|Vaal Natchathiram]]'' || rowspan=\"3\" | Shankar-Ehsaan-Loy\n|-\n|\"Ooi Ooi\"\n|-\n|\"Mannil Vinmeengal\"\n|-\n|rowspan= 8| '''2008''' || \"Kadhal Siluvayil\" || ''[[Subramaniapuram]]'' || [[James Vasanthan]]\n|-\n|\"[[Cinema Cinema]]\" || ''[[Kuselan]]'' ||G. V. Prakash Kumar\n|-\n|\"Nimirndhu Nil\" || ''[[Saroja (2008 film)|Saroja]]'' || Yuvan Shankar Raja\n|-\n|\"Hey Baby\" || ''[[Aegan]]'' || Yuvan Shankar Raja\n|-\n|\"Usilampatti Sandhayila\" || ''[[Thenavattu]]'' || Srikanth Deva\n|-\n|\"Thamizh Endral Naan\" || ''[[Silambattam (film)|Silambattam]]'' || Yuvan Shankar Raja\n|-\n|\"Emmaiyalum\" || rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[Thiruvannamalai (film)|Thiruvannamalai]]'' || rowspan=\"2\" | Srikanth Deva\n|-\n|\"Siva Siva\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\" | '''2009''' || \"Kabadi Kabadi\" || ''[[Vennila Kabadi Kuzhu]]'' || [[V. Selvaganesh]]\n|-\n|\"Oru Adangapidari\" || ''[[Siva Manasula Sakthi]]'' || Yuvan Shankar Raja\n|-\n|\"Vanga Kadal\" || ''[[1977 (film)|1977]]'' || Vidyasagar\n|-\n|\"Yavarum Nalam\" || rowspan=\"4\" | ''[[Yavarum Nalam]]'' || rowspan=\"4\" | Shankar-Ehsaan-Loy\n|-\n|\"Kaatrile Vaasame\"\n|-\n|\"Yavarum Nalam\"(Remix Version)\n|-\n|\"Kaatrile Vaasame\"(Remix Version)\n|-\n|\"Megam Pola\" || ''[[Ananda Thandavam (2009 film)|Ananda Thandavam]]'' || G. V. Prakash Kumar\n|-\n|\"Sambho Siva Sambho\" || ''[[Naadodigal]]'' || [[Sundar C Babu]]\n|-\n|\"Seene Sovu\" || ''[[Vedigundu Murugesan]]'' || Dhina\n|-\n|\"Naan Adicha\" || ''[[Vettaikaaran (2009 film)|Vettaikaaran]]'' || [[Vijay Antony]]\n|-\n|\"Dishyum Dishyum\" || ''[[Kandhakottai]]'' || Dhina\n|-\n|rowspan= 10| '''2010''' || \"Apple Laptop\" || ''[[Jaggubhai]]'' || Rafee\n|-\n|\"Oru Sooravali\" || ''[[Thamizh Padam]]'' || Kannan\n|-\n|\"Aasa Machaane\" || ''[[Kola Kolaya Mundhirika]]'' || V. Selvaganesh\n|-\n|\"Kaattu Sirukki\" || ''[[Raavanan]]'' || A. R. Rahman\n|-\n|\"Thothu Ponen\