opala\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|[[Gopika Poornima|Poornima]], [[Kalpana Raghavendar|Kalapana]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Bhalevadivi Basu]]''\n|\"Yahi Hai Right Choice\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Ammammo Bramha\"\n|[[Gopika Poornima]]\n|-\n![[Sri Manjunatha (film)|''Sri Manjunatha'']]\n|\"Om Mahaprana\"\n|[[Hamsalekha]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Srikanth (Telugu actor)|Naa Manasistha Raa]]''\n|\"Champodde\"\n|[[S. A. Rajkumar]]\n|[[Anuradha Sriram]]\n|-\n!''[[Nuvvu Naaku Nachav]]''\n|\"O Navvu Chalu\"\n|[[Saluri Koteswara Rao|Koti]]\n|\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Adhipathi]]''\n|\"Aada Brathuke\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Saluri Koteswara Rao|Koti]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Panchadara Patikabellam\"\n|Radhika\n|-\n!''[[Daddy (2001 film)|Daddy]]''\n|\"Lucky Lucky\"\n|[[S. A. Rajkumar]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Snehamante Idera]]''\n|\"Snehamunte\"\n|Shiva Shankar\n|[[Tippu (singer)|Tippu]],Krishna Raj\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Paarthale Paravasam|Paravasam]]''\n|\"Manmadha Maasam\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[A. R. Rahman]]\n|[[Nithyasree Mahadevan]]\n|-\n|\"Naadhir Dinna\" \n|[[S. P. Sailaja]]\n|-\n!''[[Bhadrachalam (film)|Badrachalam]]''\n|\"Okate Jananam\"\n|[[Vandemataram Srinivas]]\n|[[K. S. Chithra]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Star (2001 film)|Takkari Donga Chakkani Chukka]]''\n|\"Thom\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[A. R. Rahman]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Maradalive\"\n|Ganga\n|-\n![[Hanuman Junction (film)|''Hanuman Junction'']] \n|\"Kushi Kushiga\"\n|[[Suresh Peters]]\n|[[Swarnalatha]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Citizen (film)|Citizen]]''\n|\"Poojari Poojari\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Deva (composer)|Deva]]\n|[[Vasundhara Das]]\n|-\n|\"Chikki Bugga\"\n|[[Sadhana Sargam]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"18\" |2002\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Seema Simham]]''\n|\"Manchithanam\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Rendu Jalla Papa\"\n|[[K. S. Chithra]]\n|-\n!''[[Takkari Donga]]''\n|\"Naluguriki\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Seshu]]''\n|\"Sayantram Cheruvyindo\"\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|\n|-\n![[Santosham (2002 film)|''Santosham'']]\n|\"D