a Anta Krishna Anta\" ||   || Hamsalekha \n|- \n|| ''Ambi''  || \"Yede Halu\" ||  || V Nagendra Prasad \n|- \n|| ''Datta'' || \"Baare Baare\" || Malathi || R P Patnayak \n|- \n|| ''Gandugali Kumararama'' || \"Kumara Rama\" ||  || Gurukiran \n|- \n|| ''Gopi'' || \"Dum Dum Dolu\" ||  || K Kalyan \n|- \n|| ''Hatavadi'' || \"Yaru Yaru\" || Ashwath C, Jayashree B || V.Ravichandran \n|- \n|| ''Hubli'' || \"Kannada Naadina\" ||  || A R Hemanth \n|- \n|| ''Mohini 9886788888'' || \"Jwala Mukhiya Haage\" || Ratnmala || Hamsalekha \n|- \n|| ''Neenello Naanalle'' || \"Sankraanti\" ||  || Ramesh Krishna \n|- \n|| ''Ravi Shastry'' || \"Vesha Vesha\" ||  || Rajesh Ramnath \n|- \n|| ''Sevanti Sevanti'' || \"Nodavalandara\" ||  || S A Rajkumar \n|- \n|| ''Shriram'' || \"Yella Neene Thaaye\" ||  || Gurukiran \n|- \n|| ''Thayiya Madilu'' || \"Aparanji\" || Shreya Ghoshal || S A Rajkumar \n|- \n|rowspan= 13| '''2007''' || ''Baba''  || \"Surya Chandra\" ||  || Arjun\n|- \n|| ''Bhupathi''  || \"Se Se Se Nanna\" || Shamitha Malnad || V. Harikrishna \n|- \n|| ''Brindavana''  || \"Thangali\" || Hemanth Kumar, Kailash Kher, Karthik,  || V Harikrishna \n|- \n|| ''Ee Preethi Yeke Bhoomi Melide'' || \"Baarayya Baarayya\" || Supriya Acharya || R P Patnayak \n|- \n|| ''Ekangi''  || \"Banna Bannada Loka\" ||  || V.Ravichandran \n|- \n|| ''Gaja''  || \"Aitalakadi\" || Shamita Malnad || V Harikrishna \n|- \n|| ''[[Geleya]]'' || \"Chaangu Bala Chaangure\" ||  || Mano Murthy \n|- \n|| ''Gooli'' || \"Deelige Deelu\" || KS. Chithra, Sathya P, Sudeep || Anoop Seelin (HP) \n|- \n|| ''Gopi'' || \"Maleyu Ide\" ||  || K Kalyan \n|- \n|| ''Hatavadi'' || \"Ata Udugatavo\" ||  || V.Ravichandran \n|- \n|| ''Parodi'' || \"Cool Drinks\" ||  || Rajesh Ramanath \n|- \n|| ''Ravi Shastry'' || \"Vesha Vesha Remix\" ||  || Rajesh Ramnath \n|- \n|| ''Ugaadi'' || \"Dhin Dhinak Diri Nakdithom\" ||  || R P Patnayak \n|- \n|rowspan= 16| '''2008''' || ''Aathmeeya''  || \"Aa Bili Bili Modana\" ||  || Manoj George \n|- \n|| ''A