i]]''\n|\"Champakamala\"\n|Kamalakar\n|[[Malathy Lakshman|Malathi]]\n|-\n!''[[Jai Chiranjeeva]]''\n|\"Thillana Dhintanana\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Majaa]]''\n|\"Chi Chi Chi\"\n|[[Vidyasagar (composer)|Vidyasagar]]\n|[[Harini (singer)|Harini]]\n|-\n!''[[Sada Mee Sevalo]]''\n|\"Lub Dub\"\n|[[Vandemataram Srinivas]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"20\" |2006\n!''[[Style (2006 film)|Style]]''\n|\"Raa Raa Raa\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Lakshmi (2006 film)|Lakshmi]]''\n|\"Hey Sathyabhama\"\n|[[Ramana Gogula]]\n|Sudha\n|-\n!''[[Manasu Palike Mouna Raagam]]''\n|\"Thelusuko Jeevitham\"\n|[[K. M. Radha Krishnan]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Raam (2006 film)|Raam]]''\n|\"Made In Hyderabad\"\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Sri Ramadasu]]''\n|\"Isvakulaku\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Allah Rama\"\n|[[Vijay Yesudas]]\n|-\n!''[[Happy (2006 film)|Happy]]''\n|\"Nee Kosam\"\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|\n|-\n![[Veerabhadra (film)|''Veerabhadra'']]\n|\"Janam Kosam\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Godavari (film)|Godavari]]''\n|\"Manasa Gelupu\"\n|[[K. M. Radha Krishnan]]\n|[[K. S. Chithra]]\n|-\n!''[[Astram (film)|Astram]]''\n|\"Raa Chilaka\"\n|[[S. A. Rajkumar]]\n|[[Sujatha Mohan]]\n|-\n!''[[Stalin (2006 film)|Stalin]]''\n|\"Parare Parare\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Nuvvu Nennu Prema]]''\n|\"Bangaranni Bangaranni\"\n|[[A. R. Rahman]]\n|[[Sunitha Sarathy]]\n|-\n!''[[Raraju (2006 film)|Raaraju]]''\n|\"Vasthandhi\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|[[Anuradha Sriram]]\n|-\n![[Mayabazar (2006 film)|''Mayabazar'']]\n|\"Nadume Chitikantha\"\n|[[K. M. Radha Krishnan]]\n|[[K. S. Chithra]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" |''[[Khatarnak]]''\n|\"Dhoma Kudithe\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[K. S. Chithra]]\n|-\n|\"Vesthaavaa\"\n|-\n|\"Bujji Bujji Papa\"\n|Gayatri R, Noel\n|-\n!''[[Rakhi (2006 film)|Rakhi]]''\n|\"Ninnu Chuste\"\n|[[Devi Sri Prasad]]\n|[[Gopika Poornima]]\n|-\n!''[[Poi (film)|Abaddam]]''\n|\"Ichatey Ichatey\" \n|[[Vidyasagar (composer)|Vidyasagar]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Annavaram (film)|Annavaram]]''\n|\"Raakshasa Rajyam\"\n|[[Ramana Gogula]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"18\" |2007\n![[Yogi (2007 film)|''Yogi'']]\n|\"Dolu Baja\"\n|[[Ramana Gogula]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Poramboku]]''\n|\"Bangaram Ithey\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Maharathi (2007 film)|Maharathi]]''\n|\"Uppu Chepa Pappu Chaaru\"\n|[[Gurukiran]]\n|B Jayasree\n|-\n!''[[Ta Ra Rum Pum]]''\n|\"Naatho Forever\"\n|[[Vishal\u2013Shekhar]]\n|[[Shreya Ghoshal]]\n|-\n![[Lakshmi Kalyanam (2007 film)|''Lakshmi Kalyanam'']]\n|\"Bava Bava\"\n|[[R. P. Patnaik]]\n|[[Sujatha Mohan]]\n|-\n!''[[Munna (2007 film)|Munna]]''\n|\"Baga Baga\"\n|[[Harris Jayaraj]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Aata]]''\n|\"Aata\"\n|[[Devi Sri Prasad]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Johnny Gaddaar]]''\n|\"Move Your Body\"\n|[[Shankar\u2013Ehsaan\u2013Loy]]\n|[[Nandini Srikar]]\n|-\n!''[[Shankar Dada Zindabad]]''\n|\"Good Morning Hyderabad\"\n|[[Devi Sri Prasad]]\n|Divya\n|-\n!''[[Yamadonga]]''\n|\"Young Yama\"\n|[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n|[[Mano (singer)|Mano]], [[M. M. Keeravani|Keeravani]],Pranavi\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Vel (film)|Deva]]''\n|\"Kondapalli Nimmakaaya\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|[[Anuradha Sriram]]\n|-\n|\"Palakonda Kona Lona\" \n|\n|-\n!''[[Vijayadasami (film)|Vijayadasami]]''\n|\"Raa Raa\"\n|[[Srikanth Deva]]\n|\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Don (2007 film)|Don]]''\n|\"Su Su Suriyanna\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Raghava Lawrence]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Dhada Puttista\"\n|\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" |''[[Taare Zameen Par|Nela Meeda Thaaralu]]''\n|\"Meghala\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Shankar\u2013Ehsaan\u2013Loy]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Ennadu Amma Cheppale\"\n|\n|-\n|\"Why Why Can't You\"\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" |2008\n!''[[Krishnarjuna]]''\n|\"A A Aa E Ee\"\n|[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n|\n|-\n!''[[Kantri]]''\n|\"Raamare\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|[[Sunidhi Chauhan]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Pandurangadu]]''\n|\"Sahasra Sheerasha\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n|\n|-\n|\"Sri Sri Sri Rajadhi Raja\"\n|[[Geetha Madhuri]]\n|-\n!''[[Kathanayakudu (2008 fi